{"tid":2184543,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"一個人去食飯","createTime":"2020-09-01T15:15:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T15:25:28.000Z","uid":24400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"94b222a6490c6a4a386a19740b6528d8b45d53f1","tid":2184543,"uid":24400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:15:52.000Z","msg":"有好多次打電話book位<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n餐廳：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n餐廳：你幾多位？<br />\n我：一位<br />\n餐廳：請留個電話<br />\n我：xxxxxxxx<br />\n餐廳：你幾多位？<br />\n我：一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問多次<br />\n好似專登為難我咁<br />\n我都知香港做餐廳唔容易<br />\n我一個人去坐二人嘅位好似真係唔係幾好咁<br />\n<br />\n但其實有冇諗過呢個社會越來越多人單身<br />\n好有必要整一個人嘅位呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229f4839c829f7924198695a288200b4ac943b29","tid":2184543,"uid":323366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:18:50.000Z","msg":"自己一個早餐lunch好似冇咁awkward<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e929b82a9b4c34bb0008e987c399fc7f1cf523ca","tid":2184543,"uid":24400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"229f4839c829f7924198695a288200b4ac943b29","tid":2184543,"uid":323366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:18:50.000Z","msg":"自己一個早餐lunch好似冇咁awkward<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:25:28.000Z","msg":"去啲好少少嘅餐廳<br />\n就會成日發覺冇咩係一個人食飯"}]}